title: Eps. 155 - Flu Game
description:
On today’s podcast the guys talk about a characteristic that some of us struggle with. Confidence. How many of you are confident in your talents ? Confident in your abilities ? CJ notices that ET has been more confident this year than he’s been prior and on the flip side Karl admits to struggling with his own confidence. CJ steers the conversation in a way that will help listeners fix their confidence, while embracing their strengths and not focusing on their weaknesses.
